  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In GOPOGO, you play as a frog on a pogostick. Complete challenging levels and race other frogs, unlock hats and explore a big world as a small frog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10+ challenging levels to complete, each has a race challenge that follows</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play with friends in Multiplayer with Proximity Chat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-  Collect Golden Lilypads to Unlock Hats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Original Drum and Bass Soundtrack and Piano music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Level Replay System, watch your run after finishing a level</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In GOPOGO, you play as a frog on a pogostick. Complete challenging levels and race other frogs, unlock hats and explore a big world as a small frog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10+ challenging levels to complete, each has a race challenge that follows</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play with friends in Multiplayer with Proximity Chat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-  Collect Golden Lilypads to Unlock Hats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Original Drum and Bass Soundtrack and Piano music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Level Replay System, watch your run after finishing a level</p>",
